You can even adapt the fit thanks to the adjustable cuffs and drawcord at the hem, so you'll always feel comfortable with it on. 2 lower pockets and a chest pocket mean you have enough space to store your must have items on you without worrying about them falling out thanks to the zip fastenings.

Additionally, one of the pockets acts as a stuff sack allowing you to fold the coat and pack it away and stash it your car or attach it to your rucksack.

The Digby men's Down Jacket is a versatile and smart choice.

  • Grown on Hood
  • 3 Low Profile Zip Pockets
  • Low Profile Front Zip
  • Matching Binding at Cuffs
  • Drawcord at Hem
  • Stuff Sack in Pocket


Fabric: Woven, Shell 100% Polyamide, Lining 100% Polyamide 380T, Downproof Lining, Filling 80% Down / 20% Feather

The Thermal Grip Glove is perfect for construction, transportation, refuse collection, maintenance and local authority work. This glove has a warm acrylic 10 gauge liner and is ideal for more heavy duty, outdoor tasks or those people working in cold conditions.

When cold thermal hazards are present, the hands' motor skills can be greatly reduced, this leads to increased risks of accidents and injury. Specially designed thermal protective gloves are available to combat these hazardous environments.

Body HTML:
The Unite360 unisex thermal set should be the first thing you pack for your next ski trip. The top has a high neck with a half zip feature, great for controlling airflow. With long sleeves for extra warmth and coverage, flat seams ensure complete comfort whilst on.

Fitted with an elasticated waist, the bottoms offer a comfortable fit that also allows for a range of movement. Plus, Quick Dry fabric technology wicks away sweat to help maintain freshness and minimise dampness.

The thermal set weighs 170gsm and is super-soft, making it extremely comfortable and easy to wear whilst doing lengthy activities. So keep warm and snug during a chilly UK winter ski season in the cold with our Unite360 thermal set.

Title: Mens Trespass Vander Softshell Jacket
Body HTML:
Mens Trespass Softshell Jacket - Vander

A lightweight, softshell jacket that is surprisingly hardy. Both smart and casual, it looks great in summer, and for chillier months, it looks equally cool worn under a heavier jacket or over a few layers. Softshell clothing is somewhat of an all-rounder. A new take on classic hard shell outerwear, the material offers a more flexible experience that makes it ideal for sports, activewear, golfing and even your everyday. Our softshell jackets may not feature taped seams but they are highly technically tested to ensure that our jackets will keep you comfortable and dry during rain showers.

Features:

  • Windproof
  • Lightweight
  • Chin guard
  • Two zipped side pockets
  • Draw cord at hem
  • Adjustable cuff with tab

Fabric:

  • Woven
  • 94% Polyester, 6% Elastane

Title: Kids Trespass GLEBE II Mid Cut Boot
Body HTML:
Kids Trespass Walking Boots - GLEBE II

The Glebe II kid's hiking boots will allow them to pursue any adventure on foot in comfort and with confidence.

Fitted with an ankle cushioned collar and arch stabilising shank, they'll be completely supported when out hiking on various types of terrain. Furthermore, an all-round mud-guard shields their feet from knocks and bangs while a cushioned footbed stops aches and pains even when out exploring for longer periods.

They'll also receive waterproof protection so they'll not have damp feet and socks slowing them down. Plus, a mesh lining means air is still allowed inside to stop condensation build-up for a continuously fresh and dry feeling.

A durable outsole will help them keep balanced by providing them with good traction and the indents of the sole stop mud or debris from getting clogged up. Available in a choice of 2 colours, the Glebe II kid's hiking boots are a solid piece of hiking footwear that will see them through even the toughest of hikes.

Features:

  • Waterproof
  • Breathable
  • Mid-cut hiking boot
  • Waterproof & breathable membrane
  • Gusseted tongue
  • Protective and durable all-round mudguard
  • Ankle supportive cushioned collar and tongue
  • Arch stabilising and supportive steel shank
  • Cushioned footbed

Title: Mens Portwest KX3 Ultrasonic Tunnel Jacket
Body HTML:
The Ultrasonic Tunnel Jacket provides outstanding warmth and insulation. This style uses revolutionary heat seal construction to form the baffle lines. Bonding the fabric without stitching or thread improves the water resistance and the chances of filling, clumping or shifting is completely reduced.

Features:

  • Premium water resistant fabric
  • Heat sealed seams for increased water and wind resistance
  • Fully lined and padded to trap the heat and increase warmth
  • Elasticated cuffs for a secure fit
  • Drawcord adjustable hem
  • 5 pockets for ample storage
  • Concealed mobile phone pocket
  • Zipped pockets
  • Inner soft Insulatex lining offering warmth and comfort
  • Easy grip pullers attached to all zips
  • Chin guard with internal storm flap provides extra comfort

Fabric:

  • Shell: 100% Polyester 65g
  • Lining: 100% Polyester 65g
  • Filling: Insulatex Lining 260g

Title: Ladies Fawsley Long Length Waterproof Boots

 Waterproof & Breathable: Crafted from high-quality leather, these boots are fully waterproof, keeping your feet dry in all conditions. The breathable design ensures maximum comfort by allowing air circulation, keeping your feet fresh even after a long day outdoors.

  • Leather Upper: The premium leather upper not only looks stylish but also offers long-lasting durability, making these boots a timeless addition to your wardrobe.

Title: REGATTA TRJ513R Workwear Coveralls
Body HTML:
Stay protected and comfortable on the job with the Regatta Professional Men's TRJ513R Zip Fasten Coveralls. Designed with durability and ease of movement in mind, these coveralls are ideal for various work environments, from construction to maintenance tasks.

Key Features:

  • Polycotton Blend: Made from a 65% polyester and 35% cotton blend, these overalls are both comfortable and tough enough to handle everyday wear and tear.
  • Zip Fastening: Easy-to-use front zip closure ensures quick and secure wear.
  • Part-Elasticated Waist: Offers flexibility and allows the overalls to move with you, providing extra comfort during long work shifts.
  • Protective Design: Perfect for keeping your base layers clean and free from debris or stains while working.
  • Leg Length: Regular 31 inches inside leg length.

Built by Regatta Professional for reliability, the TRJ513R Coveralls are the go-to choice for those seeking long-lasting protection and all-day comfort in any work setting.

Title: Unisex Kids Junior Seedling Stud Coveralls
Body HTML:
Equip your little one for the outdoors with the Regatta Professional Unisex Kids Junior Seedling Stud Coveralls. These durable coveralls are designed to handle the rough and tumble of junior adventures, whether on the farm, at play, or in the garden.

Key Features:

  • Elasticated & Adjustable Waist: Offers a flexible fit for growing kids.
  • Reflective Piping: Added safety in low light environments.
  • Multiple Pockets: 1 chest pocket, 1 upper sleeve pocket, and 2 back pockets provide ample storage.
  • Concealed Snap Front Fastening: Quick and easy to put on or remove.
  • Hardwearing Polycotton Fabric: Made from 65% polyester and 35% cotton for a comfortable yet durable wear. Fabric weight: 245 GSM.
  • One Leg Length: Comes in a single standard leg length to ensure a uniform fit.

Built for comfort and practicality, these coveralls are perfect for any active child who loves to get stuck in!
